  "title": "Strong Hold Acrylic Gold Liquid Adhesive",
  "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><span>Acrylic-based LuxHair' Gold Hair Adhesive allows hair prostheses, wigs, and hair extensions to be attached to the scalp for up to two weeks.</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Advantages</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Transparent.</li>\n<li>Extra resistant to water and sweat.</li>\n<li>Hold: up to two weeks.</li>\n<li>Easy to clean.</li>\n<li>Specific formulation for hair bonding: hair prosthesis, wigs, and extensions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Format</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<p>Bottle with a brush for easy application.</p>\n<p>Quantity: 15 ml.</p>\n<p>\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Recommendations for use</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Apply to the scalp and not to the hair system.</li>\n<li>Apply to the outer edge of the desired area to be bonded.\u00a0Then spread the product evenly, applying the right amount to create a thin layer.</li>\n<li>Applying at least 2 or 3 layers is highly recommended, allowing the glue to dry 2-3 minutes between each coat application.</li>\n<li>Allow the glue to dry for a few minutes before attaching your capillary system.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle et_pb_module et_pb_accordion_item et_pb_accordion_item_3 et_clickable et_pb_toggle_open\">\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Product safety data sheet</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://luxhair.es/en/Product/luxhair-gold-liquid-adhesive#:~:text=safety%20data%20sheet-,Link,-Related%20products\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Link</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul></ul>",
